# Security

## Hard rules for Step 2

1. exactly one allowed number
2. no wildcards
3. no replies to unknown senders
4. no auto-trusting new users
5. number configured locally, not via prompt

## Out of scope (future steps)

* multi-user support
* per-group ACLs
* roles/admin permissions
* safety-number authorization
* onboarding new contacts through the agent

